OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally dry and in the
OL,6,Fsouth locally warm day, with sunny
OL,7,Fspells building into the afternoon.
OL,8,FHowever some early showers across the
OL,9,Fcloudier north. Winds northerly
OL,10,Frelatively light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry with late
OL,13,Fsunshine then clear spells always more
OL,14,Fprolonged towards the southern end of
OL,15,Fthe Great Glen. North to northeast
OL,16,Fwinds occasionally fresh across the
OL,17,FHebrides.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
