OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,6,Fweather in prospect with most dry with
OL,7,Fperiods of sunshine widespread through
OL,8,Fthe morning, before turning hazy from
OL,9,Fthe west during the afternoon. Winds
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,13,Fchange to more unsettled conditions
OL,14,Fwith a series of rain bands crossing
OL,15,Ffrom the west. However, with winds
OL,16,Fstaying southwesterly temperatures a
OL,17,Flittle up on the seasonal averages.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
